41 void kalmanFilter::prediction()
42 {
43 ROS_INFO("Prediction");
44 double delt = 1 / 14.0; // This is hardcoded, its basically message frequency or stamp diff
45 Eigen::MatrixXd At(7,7);
46 // x,y,xd,yd,volx,voly,volz
47 At << 1,0,delt,0,0,0,0,
48 0,1,0,delt,0,0,0,
49 0,0,1,0 ,0,0,0,
50 0,0,0,1 ,0,0,0,
51 0,0,0,0 ,1,0,0,
52 0,0,0,0 ,0,1,0,
53 0,0,0,0 ,0,0,1;
54 //Bt = 0;
55 mean_p_ = At*mean_;
56 ROS_INFO("Formed mean_p");
57 Eigen::MatrixXd Rt(7,7);
58 // Process noise lets say 1m for position + 0.07*noise_in_velocity =~ 2?
59 double acc = 0.1; // Process noise could be acceleration term
60 Rt << pow(delt,4)*acc,0, pow(delt,3)*acc/2,0, 0,0,0,
61 0,pow(delt,4)*acc, 0,pow(delt,3)*acc/2, 0,0,0,
62 0,0, delt*delt*acc,0, 0,0,0,
63 0,0, 0,delt*delt*acc, 0,0,0,
64 0,0, 0,0, 0.1,0,0,
65 0,0, 0,0, 0,0.1,0,
66 0,0, 0,0, 0,0,0.1;
67 cov_p_ = At*cov_*At.transpose() + Rt;
68 }

70 void kalmanFilter::measurementUpdate(Eigen::MatrixXd measurement)
71 {
72 Eigen::MatrixXd Ct(7,7);
73 Ct = Eigen::MatrixXd::Identity(7,7);
74 Eigen::MatrixXd Kgain(7,7);
75 Eigen::MatrixXd Qt(7,7);
76 //Qt = Eigen::MatrixXd::Identity(7,7); // We measure all..
77 // Estimated standard devs for this task
78 // Position +-2m ( Check catalog for this)
79 // velocity 0.5m/s lets say
80 // Volume similary lets take it as +-2m
81 // Values down belwo are squared values of stddev -> variance.
82 Qt << 4,0, 0,0, 0,0,0,
83 0,4, 0,0, 0,0,0,
84 0,0, 0.25,0, 0,0,0,
85 0,0, 0,0.25, 0,0,0,
86 0,0, 0,0, 0.2,0,0,
87 0,0, 0,0, 0,0.2,0,
88 0,0, 0,0, 0,0,0.2; // std dev of volume fields is 0.4m
89 Kgain = cov_p_*Ct.transpose()*((Ct*cov_p_*Ct.transpose()+Qt).inverse());
90
91 mean_ = mean_p_ + Kgain*(measurement - Ct*mean_p_);
92 cov_ = (Eigen::MatrixXd::Identity(7,7) - Kgain*Ct)*cov_p_;
93 }
